<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <title>Chat Ups As A Service</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/bootstrap/css/bootstrap.css"/>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/nerd.css" type="text/css"/>
</head>

<body>

    <div class="container">

        <form class="navbar-form pull-right navbar-fixed-bottom" method="post" action="/nerd/<%= @to %>/<%= @from %>">
            <input type="text" class="span3" name="email">
            <button type="submit" class="btn">Send Page</button>
        </form>

        <div class="row-fluid">

            <div class="span8 offset2 words">

                <h1>Me without you, <%= @to.capitalize %>, is like a nerd without braces, a shoe without laces, asentencewithoutspaces.</h1>
                <p><em>from <%= @from.capitalize %></em></p>

            </div>
            
        </div>

    </div>

</body>


</html>